{"title":"桥（外一首）","authors":["王树品"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王树品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河水，象把剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把个山村劈两半；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南是村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江北是田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下田田不远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔水如隔天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早上要下田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村口排队等渡船；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇呀摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇到红日高三竿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田里的稻子炸了穗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树上的果子落了蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上要回村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江边等渡船；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇呀摇，摇到月牙上东山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷了粘糕凉了饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等奶的孩子哭声咽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河水啊波浪翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇了一年又一年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斧劈江水啊，水不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民盼桥啊，眼望穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军练兵进了山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河岸边扎营盘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夯声激起千尺浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一架长虹落人间！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大人孩子桥上走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支山歌飘云间："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“解放军架桥恩情长哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚河水流不断……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱民河爱民河，长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲曲弯弯向东方；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下游驻着解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上游有个王大娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘养了一群鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天戏水河中央；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然大雨发洪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪打鸭群下海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士一见忙下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管河深浪涛狂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只一只救上岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻路送还王大娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了夏天秋风凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭子长得肥又胖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年老不怕道路远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘军营看儿郎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提了两只大公鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭蛋煮上一箩筐："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这是大娘一片心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人一个快尝尝。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士接过鸭和蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒茶让坐叫大娘："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“多谢大娘疼孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练好本领保国防。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘回家喜洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个战士等门旁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个提着两只鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个背着蛋一筐。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}